  - type: en-US
    strings:
    # ┌─┐┬┌─┐┌┬┐┌─┐┬
    # ├─┘│└─┐ │ │ ││
    # ┴  ┴└─┘ ┴ └─┘┴─┘
      STR_PISTOL_UFOPEDIA: The standard issue XCom pistol is a high powered semi-automatic with a 15 round capacity.
    # ┬─┐┬┌─┐┬  ┌─┐┌─┐
    # ├┬┘│├┤ │  ├┤ └─┐
    # ┴└─┴└  ┴─┘└─┘└─┘
      # AUTOMATIC RILE
      STR_AUTOMATIC_RIFLE: Automatic Rifle
      STR_AUTOMATIC_RIFLE_UFOPEDIA: This powerful battle rifle takes 7.62mm ammunition in 20 round clips. While powerful, it has high recoil.
      # AUTOMATIC RIFLE/GRENADE LAUNCHER
      STR_RIFLE_GRENADE: Automatic Rifle/Grenade
      STR_RIFLE_GRENADE_UFOPEDIA: This rifle has increased firepower with underrail attached grenade launcher.
      # MARKSMAN'S RIFLE
      STR_MARKSMANS_RIFLE: Marksman's Rifle
      STR_MARKSMANS_RIFLE_UFOPEDIA: This highly accurate rifle has scope and is suitable to aid XCom soldiers during mid range combat.
    # ┌─┐─┐ ┬┌─┐┬  ┌─┐┌─┐┬┬  ┬┌─┐┌─┐
    # ├┤ ┌┴┬┘├─┘│  │ │└─┐│└┐┌┘├┤ └─┐
    # └─┘┴ └─┴  ┴─┘└─┘└─┘┴ └┘ └─┘└─┘
      # HEAVY CANNON
      STR_HEAVY_CANNON_UFOPEDIA: The heavy cannon is a devastating, but cumbersome, weapon. Its versatility comes from the fact that it can take multiple types of ammunition - for example incendiary and high explosive.
      # ROCKET LAUNCHER
      STR_LARGE_ROCKET: HEAT Rocket
      STR_ROCKET_LAUNCHER_UFOPEDIA: The rocket launcher is a laser guided system which can fire multiple different sizes of missile. Given time, it can even control missile's flight time, allowing to attack enemies with indirect fire.
